Technical Notes
- Stack
  - Backend: Java 17, Spring Boot 3.x, Spring Security, Spring Data JPA, MapStruct (optional), Validation (jakarta), Lombok, JWT (jjwt), MySQL 8.
  - Frontend: React 18 + Vite, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui, React Query, React Router, Axios, Recharts/Chart.js.
  - Infrastructure: .env for DB/keys; Docker Compose (optional) for MySQL.
- Security
